/href></Icon></IconStyle><LineStyle><color>ff2b5a7d</color><width>3</width></LineStyle></Style><Folder><name>1. Telemachus</name><Placemark><name>The Joyce Tower, Sandycove</name><description><![CDATA[<b>8am</b><br>Stephen, Mulligan and Haines lodge in the Martello tower; the novel opens on its gun-platform.<br><i>Stately, plump Buck Mulligan came from the stairhead, bearing a bowl of lather on which a mirror and a razor lay crossed. (1.1)</i>]]></description><styleUrl>#ep1</styleUrl><ExtendedData><Data name="work"><value>Ulysses</value></Data><Data name="group"><value>1</value></Data><Data name="kind"><value>place</value></Data><Data name="time"><value>8am</value></Data><Data name="gloss"><value>Stephen, Mulligan and Haines lodge in the Martello tower; the novel opens on its gun-platform.</value></Data><Data name="quote"><value>Stately, plump Buck Mulligan came from the stairhead, bearing a bowl of lather on which a mirror and a razor lay crossed.</value></Data><Data name="ref"><value>1.1</value></Data><Data name="name"><value>The Joyce Tower, Sandycove</value></Data></ExtendedData><Point><coordinates>-6.113608,53.288671,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>The Forty Foot</name><description><![CDATA[<b>8am</b><br>The men's bathing place just below the tower, where Mulligan goes down to swim — 'the snotgreen sea, the scrotumtightening sea.']]></description><styleUrl>#ep1</styleUrl><ExtendedData><Data name="work"><value>Ulysses</value></Data><Data name="group"><value>1</value></Data><Data name="kind"><value>place</value></Data><Data name="time"><value>8am</value></Data><Data name="gloss"><value>The men's bathing place just below the tower, where Mulligan goes down to swim — 'the snotgreen sea, the scrotumtightening sea.'</value></Data><Data name="name"><value>The Forty Foot</value></Data></ExtendedData><Point><coordinates>-6.113699,53.289486,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Stephen's morning: to the Forty Foot</name><description><![C