239241,53.346054,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Westland Row Post Office</name><description><![CDATA[<b>9.45am</b><br>Bloom collects Martha Clifford's letter under the name Henry Flower.]]></description><styleUrl>#ep5</styleUrl><ExtendedData><Data name="work"><value>Ulysses</value></Data><Data name="group"><value>5</value></Data><Data name="kind"><value>place</value></Data><Data name="time"><value>9.45am</value></Data><Data name="gloss"><value>Bloom collects Martha Clifford's letter under the name Henry Flower.</value></Data><Data name="name"><value>Westland Row Post Office</value></Data></ExtendedData><Point><coordinates>-6.249887,53.339917,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark><Placemark><name>Sweny's Pharmacy</name><description><![CDATA[<b>9.45am</b><br>Bloom buys the cake of lemon soap he carries through the day.]]></description><styleUrl>#ep5</styleUrl><ExtendedData><Data name="work"><value>Ulysses</value></Data><Data name="group"><value>5</value></Data><Data name="kind"><value>place</value></Data><Data name="time"><value>9.45am</value></Data><Data name="gloss"><value>Bloom buys the cake of lemon soap he carries through the day.</value></Data><Data name="name"><value>Sweny's Pharmacy</value></Data></ExtendedData><Point><coordinates>-6.250551,53.34187,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark></Folder><Folder><name>6. Hades</name><Placemark><name>Paddy Dignam's house</name><description><![CDATA[<b>11am</b><br>The funeral procession sets out from the dead man's house in Sandymount.]]></description><styleUrl>#ep6</styleUrl><ExtendedData><Data name="work"><value>Ulysses</value></Data><Data name="group"><value>6</value></Data><Data name="kind"><value>place</value></Data><Data name="time"><value>11am</value></Data><Data name="gloss"><value>The funeral procession sets out from the dead man's house in Sandymount.</value></Data><Data name="name"><value>Paddy Dignam's house</value></Data></ExtendedData><Point><coordinates>-6.223359,53.335519,0</coordinates></P